.000Z","msg":"宋康昊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 影帝真係唔係浪得虛名 <br />\n殺人回憶 韓流怪嚇 復仇 親切的金子 逆權大狀<br />\n每一套都好睇<br />\n<br />\n遲啲睇埋呢套同密陽"},{"pid":"68908aa5f1cb9574f58e9bbb55dfa9cfef2b505e","tid":395190,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T17:16:09.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"5f282cc52a0ab665f2ccdd271ee1ef6c9f0c7b2a","tid":395190,"uid":25164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:07:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隔離個女仔都睇到喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申一個人去睇</span></blockquote><br />\n你係韓國睇?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港M_ _同另一間星期六日都有先上幾場呀 ～"},{"pid":"d614bdfa93ae6391d6ddbc6f9931d6914a6fb378","tid":395190,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:10:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔係大制作<br />\n名又改得差<br />\n港豬唔會理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地揸車啲鏡頭都真係幾膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港發行都做得好差<br />\n個名擺明求鳩其改<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66fab9b7498c134cb4a7315aa3030bc6dbd38bc","tid":395190,"uid":25164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:21:49.000Z","msg":"呢個名我睇完都記唔到<br />\n<br />\n譯做<span style=\"color: red;\">《的士佬》</span>算啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&hellip;不過會即刻聯想到香港的士佬</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/KOrZem9QJdU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FKOrZem9QJdU&d=2PyxKiLoDX3QrqGFxE08Vy7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=96a776eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/KOrZem9QJdU</a>"},{"pid":"bdb638ab4ac917c751424b8f9d1ac0fb585a3087","tid":395190,"uid":30478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T15:17:28.000Z","msg":"好好睇<br />\n同埋真係要睇，反省自己當下既狀況<br />\n今日既自由係前人用生命換返黎"},{"pid":"beeb791d766f514a83108ec5d3ebe30959344ce8","tid":395190,"uid":129525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T17:12:50.000Z","msg":"睇到喊加一 好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}